 tag or not and in case of clashes, a warning should be thrown. \r\n\r\n\r\n","score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/gohugoio/hugo/issues/4676","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/gohugoio/hugo","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/gohugoio/hugo/issues/4676/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/gohugoio/hugo/issues/4676/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/gohugoio/hugo/issues/4676/events","html_url":"https://github.com/gohugoio/hugo/issues/4676","id":318254774,"number":4676,"title":"hugo server reload issue","user":{"login":"lincryption","id":38738493,"avatar_url":"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/38738493?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/lincryption","html_url":"https://github.com/lincryption","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lincryption/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lincryption/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lincryption/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lincryption/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lincryption/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lincryption/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lincryption/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lincryption/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lincryption/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":1,"created_at":"2018-04-27T02:13:23Z","updated_at":"2018-05-11T20:05:51Z","closed_at":"2018-05-11T20:05:51Z","author_association":"NONE","body":"(May be Google Chrome issue)\r\nFiles which are used by `hugo server` are somehow cached. Sometimes during building `hugo server` uses old cached files instead of new.\r\n\r\nIn my case, `static\\css\\styles.css` did not reload. The server used old cached styles (html always  reloaded as expected and was up to date). At the same time, `hugo` worked as expected so `public\\css\\styles.css` was up to date.\r\n\r\n**To replicate:**\r\n1) Run `hugo server`, then Ctrl+C\r\n2) Edit css file (for example, change font)\r\n3) Run `hugo server`\r\n4) Styles remain the same as before\r\n\r\n\"Clear storage\" via Chrome developer tools and multiple rebuildings with `hugo server --disableFastRender` did not solve the issue.\r\n\r\nSolved by editing css file while `hugo server` was running.\r\n\r\nHugo v0.40\r\nhttps://github.com/lincryption/delta-hugo\r\nWindows 10 Enterprise Version 10.0.16299 Build 16299\r\nGoogle Chrome Version 65.0.3325.181 (Official Build) (64-bit)","score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/gohugoio/hugo/issues/4675","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/gohugoio/hugo","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/gohugoio/hugo/issues/4675/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/gohugoio/hugo/issues/4675/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/gohugoio/hugo/issues/4675/events","html_url":"https://github.com/gohugoio/hugo/issues/4675","id":318254156,"number":4675,"title":".WordCount, .FuzzyWordCount, .ReadingTime is not set on posts with <!--more-->","user":{"login":"timshannon","id":1330485,"avatar_url":"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/1330485?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/timshannon","html_url":"https://github.com/timshannon","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timshannon/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timshannon/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timshannon/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timshannon/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timshannon/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timshannon/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timshannon/repos","ev